      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-4 bg-navy text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-navy/90 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
